have left you.

01:05:10.274 --> 01:05:11.673
- You can't just show up.

01:05:11.775 --> 01:05:13.942
- I just need five minutes,
look I got you some flowers.

01:05:14.044 --> 01:05:15.577
So this is where
you grew up huh?

01:05:17.915 --> 01:05:18.880
It's rustic.

01:05:20.450 --> 01:05:21.816
Awe.

01:05:21.919 --> 01:05:23.051
I missed you Harmony.

01:05:25.322 --> 01:05:26.688
I need you.

01:05:26.790 --> 01:05:29.124
I was just so stressed about
the record, and the label,

01:05:29.226 --> 01:05:32.294
and everything getting
so crazy I didn't realize

01:05:32.396 --> 01:05:33.995
how much I needed you.

01:05:34.097 --> 01:05:36.298
But I've been thinking a lot
about us and there's something

01:05:36.400 --> 01:05:38.600
that I should've
done a long time ago.

01:05:43.473 --> 01:05:45.073
So, what do ya say?

01:05:46.510 --> 01:05:47.409
Marry me.

01:05:49.813 --> 01:05:52.514
- Well the first batch
seems perfect if you want.

01:05:52.616 --> 01:05:54.649
- Somebody say
cookies are ready?

01:05:54.751 --> 01:05:57.619
- Mr. Collins so good to
finally meet you, I'm Devin.

