- This a bad time?

01:06:08.865 --> 01:06:11.666
- Hey, I'm Harmony's fiance.

01:06:11.768 --> 01:06:12.534
- Fiance?

01:06:12.636 --> 01:06:13.401
- Yeah.

01:06:14.471 --> 01:06:15.236
- Right.

01:06:16.640 --> 01:06:17.639
I'm gonna go.

