- Harmony, what's going on?

01:06:58.382 --> 01:07:00.815
- Honey why don't you follow me?

01:07:00.917 --> 01:07:03.051
- But I wanna know
what's going on.

01:07:05.022 --> 01:07:08.823
- Devin, you and me, we're
gonna have a talk, right now.

01:07:10.994 --> 01:07:14.629
- Okay, this way?

01:07:23.840 --> 01:07:25.707
- Why did you think it
was okay to come here?

01:07:26.576 --> 01:07:30.412
- Because I wanted to
surprise you, and I wanted

01:07:30.514 --> 01:07:32.680
