entire life by leaving you.

01:08:01.478 --> 01:08:02.777
I need you Harm.

01:08:03.980 --> 01:08:06.281
- Devin you can't just
say things like that.

01:08:06.383 --> 01:08:08.216
- Well why not?

01:08:08.318 --> 01:08:10.852
I still know that we are
meant to be together.

01:08:10.954 --> 01:08:12.887
Don't throw away
all of these years.

01:08:15.292 --> 01:08:18.725
Harmony I need you on my team.

01:08:18.828 --> 01:08:20.194
You're my number one girl.

01:08:24.600 --> 01:08:25.633
- Oh my God!

01:08:28.939 --> 01:08:30.004
Harmony are you going to
introduce us to the reason

01:08:30.107 --> 01:08:32.307
why you haven't had
time for any of us?

